In [2]:
def show_hist_by_ploty(data, col_name: str, bins=20, title=' ', label_x='X', label_y='Y', histfunc='count', x_range=[]):
    """     ploty
    """
    hist = px.histogram(data,
                        x=col_name,
                        nbins=bins,
                        histfunc=histfunc,
                        title=title,
                        range_x = x_range,
                        labels={col_name: label_x}
            )
    hist.update_yaxes(title_text=label_y)
    hist.show()
